node.text:
Fish can’t fool 9 of the world’s best anglers. But we can. Last tournament season, PowerBait MaxScent took the trails by storm, and some might say the science gave our pro anglers an unfair advantage to catching more bass. So we decided to play a little prank and “ban” the highly potent bait from @majorleaguefishingofficial . Sure it was an April fool’s joke, but the reactions are priceless!

No, PowerBait MaxScent is NOT banned by MLF, but good luck finding it on the shelf. The scientifically proven scent dispersion of PowerBait MaxScent that helps you catch 45% more fish is here to stay‼️

#berkleyfishing #catchmorefish #aprilfools

Berkley pros put on a show during the @majorleaguefishingofficial stage 5 event at Sturgeon Bay last week, with the lb. total for all Berkley pros fishing the event being over 2,400lbs of Smallmouth Bass🤯

During the Championship round, Berkley pro and 2019 MLF Redcrest Champion @edwinevers2 got to show the MLF crew in person why Berkley pros were catching more fish than everyone else on this one bait. Check it out to see for yourself the science behind PowerBait MaxScent, and why that PowerBait MaxScent Flat Worm is such an incredibly effective bait!

#BerkleyFishing #CatchMoreFish #BerkleyIcast2020 #MaxScent
